[[File:Galaxies_Opera_House_Posters.jpg|thumb|300px|Signs for ''The Menace of the Opera'' and other shows outside the Galaxies Opera House]]
'''''The Menace of the Opera''''' was a musical playing at the [[Galaxies Opera House/Legends|Galaxies Opera House]] in [[19 BBY/Legends|19 BBY]]. A sign advertising the show was displayed outside of the [[Opera/Legends|opera]] house during a performance of [[Squid Lake/Legends|''Squid Lake'']] attended by [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] and [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]]. The sign depicted an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|imperial]] [[Stormtrooper/Legends|Stormtrooper]] [[Helmet/Legends|helmet]].<ref name="Revenge of the Clone Menace">''[[Tag & Bink: Revenge of the Clone Menace]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
The play's title may have a dual reference to both [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']] and the real-world operatic musical [[Wikipedia:The Phantom of the Opera (1986 musical)|''The Phantom of the Opera'']].

